&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience in building and leading teams or volunteers, including recruiting, training, and mentoring.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient with computers and social media, and able to quickly become proficient in new technology formats.&lt;/li&gt;
