&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOB SPECS:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Classification: Full-time temporary, hourly, non-exempt&lt;br&gt;Start and End Date: Late August - Late October (12 weeks)&lt;br&gt;Location: Onsite (Port St. Lucie)&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOB SUMMARY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
