&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOB DUTIES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pastoring, serving and caring for students and their families at the campus level, while coordinating on-site services and events for the MIX.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading CFStudents weekly experiences like Wednesdays, owning the MIX experience and environments, and helping with events (Camps, Retreats, etc.) alongside other various projects within CFStudents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing and mobilizing students to lead and serve within CFStudents, and working with Campus Teams to ensure student participation in weekend worship, the Journey, 4th Saturday Serve, and CF Global events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building an extensive team of adult volunteers to invest in our students, including Service Volunteers and Group Leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
